data.description: Discover the perfect blend of serene living and modern comfort in this beautiful ranch-style home nestled on a sprawling 5-acre property within the highly regarded Jordan Elbridge School District. Inside, the open-concept living and dining areas offer abundant natural light along with 3 well-appointed bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms (w/ master ensuite). Step outside to a picturesque setting that offers endless possibilities for gardening, relaxation, outdoor gatherings, and more. Bonus: two finished basement rooms provide endless possibilities for use, whether it's a home office, gym, or playroom. An additional finished room upstairs can serve as a cozy retreat or an extra bedroom. This where you will also find a large adjacent attic area that provides plenty of room for all your storage needs. This ranch-style home is a rare find, offering not only space and comfort but also the versatility of bonus rooms and storage options to suit your lifestyle. Don't miss out on the chance to make this your own.
